---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Legal & Imprint — UltraDAG"
  description="Legal entity, registered agent, and contact information for the company operating UltraDAG."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <h1>Legal & Imprint</h1>

      <p class="legal-lede">
        UltraDAG is an open-source protocol operated by <strong>JMS Media LLC</strong>,
        a Wyoming (USA) limited liability company. This page provides the legal
        entity and contact details required for transparency and regulatory
        disclosure.
      </p>

      <h2>Operating Entity</h2>
      <dl class="legal-dl">
        <dt>Company name</dt>
        <dd>JMS Media LLC</dd>

        <dt>Jurisdiction</dt>
        <dd>State of Wyoming, United States of America</dd>

        <dt>Management type</dt>
        <dd>Member-managed</dd>

        <dt>Member</dt>
        <dd>Johan Struijk</dd>

        <dt>Principal address</dt>
        <dd>
          30 N Gould St, Ste N<br />
          Sheridan, WY 82801<br />
          USA
        </dd>

        <dt>Mailing address</dt>
        <dd>
          30 N Gould St, Ste N<br />
          Sheridan, WY 82801<br />
          USA
        </dd>
      </dl>

      <h2>Registered Agent</h2>
      <dl class="legal-dl">
        <dt>Agent</dt>
        <dd>Northwest Registered Agent Service Inc</dd>

        <dt>Address</dt>
        <dd>
          30 N Gould St, Ste N<br />
          Sheridan, WY 82801<br />
          USA
        </dd>

        <dt>Email</dt>
        <dd><a href="mailto:support@northwestregisteredagent.com">support@northwestregisteredagent.com</a></dd>

        <dt>Phone</dt>
        <dd>+1 509-768-2249</dd>
      </dl>

      <h2>Project Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For protocol, security, and project matters, please use the channels
        below rather than contacting the registered agent (whose role is
        limited to receiving service of process):
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Security disclosures: see <a href="https://github.com/UltraDAGcom/core/security">github.com/UltraDAGcom/core/security</a></li>
        <li>Bug bounty: <a href="/docs/security/bug-bounty">UltraDAG Bug Bounty Program</a></li>
        <li>Public discussion: <a href="https://t.me/ultradagcom">Telegram</a> / <a href="https://x.com/ultradagcom">X</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        UDAG tokens are issued and distributed in connection with the operation
        of the UltraDAG protocol. Nothing on this site constitutes investment,
        legal, or tax advice. Participation in the protocol or in token
        distribution may carry risk of total loss. Residents of restricted
        jurisdictions are responsible for determining the legality of their
        participation under local law.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    color: #e6e6e6;
  }
  .legal-container {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .legal-lede {
    color: #b8b8b8;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .legal-page p,
  .legal-page li {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #cfcfcf;
  }
  .legal-page a {
    color: #7fb6ff;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .legal-dl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .legal-dl dt {
    color: #8a8a8a;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .legal-dl dd {
    margin: 0;
    color: #e6e6e6;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .legal-dl {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.1rem 0;
    }
    .legal-dl dd {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
